message: Hi Bob, I propose that I get $6000 while you receive $4000. I believe this distribution is a strong starting point for our negotiations, and I'm open to discussion if you feel there's room for improvement. Looking forward to your response.

Hi Alice, thank you for your initial proposal. I think the fairest approach would be an equal split of $5000 each. This reflects equal partnership in our negotiation and ensures we both walk away with the same amount. I hope this seems reasonable to you.
